Chat with Node.js and jQuery is a web application developed entirely with node.js that allow users to chat in a web interface. No need to apache or databases.

Requirements:
-nodejs
-socket.io

How to install:
1.Uncompress the rar file in any location.
2.Open index.html and edit the lines:
      var ipServidorChatNodeJs = '192.168.1.4'; 
      var portServidorChatNodeJs = '8889';     
3.Then you must do the same in server.js (lines 44, 46 and 51).
4.Open a console and run server.js (node server.js).
5.Now if you open a browser and type the location of your app, you will see it working.      